data.description: Contact The Anthony G Team directly! Call (845) 213-1736, Text (845) 825-2106, or Email info@anthonygrealestate.com for fastest results.Totally updated & meticulously maintained 3BR, 1.5BA Tri level Townhouse. Walking distance to all shopping restaurants, post office, & mass transportation. Anderson sliders open to your beautiful backyard oasis. Just back up the truck, take out the Lazy Boy recliner and remote control and move right in because there is absolutely nothing to do. Your kids will enjoy going to school and you will too, knowing that you're in the award-winning North Rockland Schools. Call now to schedule your own private showing before this rare diamond is gone. Call Now!
